Step -1 ->:

1 - Install Terraform version v0.14.9(Follow another file InstallTerraform )
    Download from
    https://www.terraform.io/downloads.html
    https://releases.hashicorp.com/terraform/ (For Specific Version)
2 - Install Git 
    https://git-scm.com/downloads
    
Step - 2 ->
 Clone the scripts into a folder
 
Step-3->
   
   Create a service principle in azure and update in the variable.tf file
   Login into Azure ->Open Terminal in Azure -> Paste the below command -> Copy the output in a file for future reference and update in the variable.tf
   az ad sp create-for-rbac --name ServicePrincipalName
 
Step-2->
  terraform init
  
Step-3->
terraform plan


Step-4-> Create the resources from output plan

  terraform apply  
  
  Press "yes"
Stept-4 -> Finish.Go and Check in Azure 
